{"id":8039,"content":"<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT face=宋体><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></FONT></FONT><FONT face=宋体><FONT size=3><?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\" /><st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"1958\" Month=\"10\" Day=\"22\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\"><SPAN lang=EN-US>1958</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>10</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>22</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">至</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>24</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">日，时任中共中央政治局委员、国务院副总理、国防部长的彭德怀元帅来敦煌视察。虽然只有短短的三天，但他实事求是的工作作风和高尚的品德、伟大的人格，使我们永远不能忘记的！</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">彭总来敦煌，可不是因为敦煌有个举世闻名的莫高窟。主要是敦煌放出了甘肃省第一个小麦千斤县的卫星。</SPAN><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=EN-US>1958</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>8</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">月底，《甘肃日报》以两版篇幅做了专题报道，敦煌全县</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>66181</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">亩熟地小麦，平均亩产</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>1037.1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">斤。其中，最高的单产每亩竟达到了</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>3186.4</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">斤。与前一年（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>1957</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">）的平均亩产</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>294</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">斤相比，翻了三番还多。与最高单产相比荒唐到翻了十番还多。</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">有个数据可以使大家更明了一些，</SPAN><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=EN-US>1987</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>(</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">三十年后）敦煌的小麦亩产才达到</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>699</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">斤。对比一下</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>1958</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年和</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>1987</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年的生产力水平，可想而知，当时的</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">浮夸风</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">严重到一种什么程度。</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>彭总来西北视察工作，看到这个消息，再想想自家院子里的几分地的试验田肯定迷惑不解，带着这种心情以及全国出现的一些情况，下决心来敦煌看个究竟。</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><FONT face=宋体><st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"1958\" Month=\"10\" Day=\"19\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\"><SPAN lang=EN-US>1958</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>10</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>19</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">下午，中共甘肃省委秘书长万良才给时任敦煌县委副书记的刘孟晋打电话讲，彭总计划</SPAN><st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"2010\" Month=\"10\" Day=\"22\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\"><SPAN lang=EN-US>10</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>22</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">日</SPAN></st1:chsdate></FONT><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">到敦煌去，由兰州军区司令员张达志陪同，视察的日程和生活安排，先请示张司令。</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">同日下午，在省城兰州开会的县委书记黄仕福又打电话给刘孟晋说：</SPAN><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">省委通知彭德怀同志在</SPAN><st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"2010\" Month=\"10\" Day=\"22\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\"><SPAN lang=EN-US>10</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>22</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">到敦煌去，请你做好准备。到敦煌的一切活动你请示张司令员。汇报工作大的问题按县委讨论的口径说。我们县在接待工作上挨过批评，请你注意</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">。</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">敦煌县委书记黄仕福打给副书记刘孟晋的这个电话至少说明两个问题，一是安排刘孟晋按县委讨论的口径说，其实就是亩产</SPAN><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">千斤县</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">的谎言不能变。二是让刘孟晋不能把敦煌农业生产的实际情况向彭总汇报。据刘孟晋后来的回忆文章写道，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>1958</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>8</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">月，县委个别领导人听说临夏州康乐县小麦亩产过</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">长江</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">，产量还在核实，有可能达到千斤。为了超过康乐县，千方百计的凑个千斤县，抢先向省委报喜。实际上是浮夸风等</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">左</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">的错误的产物。对于这个问题，部分干部群众有议论。但都怕涉及到</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">大跃进</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">这面旗或弄不清真相，不敢公开反对。县委在讨论时有不同意见，但是属于少数。</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">真实情况是这样的，当时外界不明真相，不知道敦煌小麦的实际播种面积。但在县委常委内部是清楚的，实播面积为</SPAN><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=EN-US>11.8</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">万亩。如果把春小麦亩产都订为千斤，总产不够，影响征购粮，只好在内部凑了个熟地</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>6</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">万亩，亩产超千斤。谎言就是这样出炉的！</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>刘孟晋接到电话后，当即通知了县委副书记兼县长张福生、副县长兼公安局长贾怀登、县委秘书魏毓钟，传达了彭总来敦煌的消息。并就接待和汇报等问题做了研究和安排。</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"1958\" Month=\"10\" Day=\"22\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\"><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=EN-US>1958</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>10</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>22</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">日</SPAN></FONT></st1:chsdate><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">下午，彭总在兰州军区司令员张达志的陪同下，乘坐一辆吉普车一行四人来到敦煌。其中，包括一位司机和一位工作人员。当今，不大的官都需要警车开道、级别警卫，讲排场，摆阔气，想想我们的党把多少优良的传统丢掉了。</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">刘孟晋见到彭总，彭总说：</SPAN><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=EN-US>“··· ···</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">，初来敦煌，我们想看看，想见见群众</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">。</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">说到住宿情况，彭总说：</SPAN><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">孟晋同志不必客气，这些情况是会想到的，这比战争时期不知要强多少倍，有吃有住就行，你要搞过分了，我还要批评你</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">。</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">彭德怀手里拿着路上捡到的棉花说：</SPAN><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">我们在离敦煌县城不远的路上看到有丢失的棉花，顺手就拣了一些，农民种棉花从种到收要投入很多劳动，流不少汗水，丢失了真可惜，县委、县政府要做这个工作，教育群众爱惜自己的劳动果实，哪怕是一点也要收回来，一点都不能浪费</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">。</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>刘孟晋仔细观察了彭总：他身穿一件已经脱了绒毛的很陈旧的黄呢大衣。估计这件大衣至少穿了二十多年，里面穿着也是很陈旧的黑色毛呢中山服，戴的帽子离开了头不成帽型，帽扇是软的，脚穿一双布鞋。</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>刘孟晋回忆文章写道当晚陪彭总吃晚饭的情况是这样的：</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">当日的晚饭是按张达志司令员的安排办的。张达志司令员说：</SPAN><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">彭总生活一向很简朴，要求很严，你们越简单越好。你们吃啥就给他吃啥，吃饭只许你一人陪，绝对不能摆宴席</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">。</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">吃饭的时候，彭总见桌上的菜就对我说：</SPAN><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">你们平常就这样吃吗？</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">我说：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">是的。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">彭总说：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">我不信。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">我说：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">比我们平常吃的要好一些，但比起敦煌人接待客人的习惯来说，这还简单了一点。干部群众要让你吃好一点，吃不好，干部、群众要骂我。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">彭总说：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">不管你怎样说，这样不行，机关食堂干部这样吃，我们就怎样吃。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">第二天吃饭，我安排减少了菜。彭总吃饭时又问我：</SPAN><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">你们的机关食堂每天都这样吃吗？我不信。那好，明天中午的饭，就在你们县委食堂吃。第一，干部和我们一起吃饭，第二，机关平常吃什么我就吃什么。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>当晚，刘孟晋给彭总送去了一本《敦煌县志》，供彭总翻阅。</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"1958\" Month=\"10\" Day=\"23\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\"><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=EN-US>1958</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>10</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>23</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">日</SPAN></FONT></st1:chsdate><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">早晨，刘孟晋和张福生、贾怀登、魏毓钟等在县委招待所会议室向彭总汇报敦煌的工作情况。</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">由于敦煌县委千斤县的口径，刘孟晋不讲，是县委的决定，讲吧，又不能蒙骗中央领导。经过再三考虑，按敦煌人的说法</SPAN><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">原盘馍馍原盘端</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">。当他汇报到农业生产（包括千斤县）和获得农业丰收的重要原因时，彭总忽然从沙发背上直起身来，似乎发现了问题。停了一会插话道：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">粮食打多少，就报多少，要实事求是。农业生产要走上步看下步，今年为明年打好基础，做好准备，这一点很重要。粮食生产要抓紧，有了粮就好办，没有粮就不安宁，要把粮食都收回来，不要浪费。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">在刘孟晋汇报到敦煌县实行了一县一社（人民公社）时，彭总插话说：</SPAN><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">我不懂，我想一县一社不是方向，不是大了就好，要看生产水平。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">在刘孟晋汇报到敦煌县正在试行吃饭等二十包以及出现的问题时，彭总插话说：</SPAN><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">包不了就不要勉强，超越现实就要碰壁。共产主义要有高度的觉悟，物质的极大丰富，没有这个基础是不行的。</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">汇报结束后，刘孟晋请彭总做指示，彭总只说了一句话：</SPAN><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">你们很辛苦！</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">便不再说话。刘孟晋从彭总的表情上看，彭总好像有说不出的焦虑和不安。他认为，彭总对部分的工作是不满意的。</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT face=宋体><FONT size=3><st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"2010\" Month=\"10\" Day=\"23\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\"><SPAN lang=EN-US>10</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>23</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">下午，刘孟晋陪同彭总到敦煌县杨家桥大队（即现在的杨家桥乡）视察。彭总仔细查看了农民集体食堂、缝纫厂、敬老院、幼儿园等。大队的领导要汇报工作，彭总拒绝了，彭总说：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">我想看看！</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">视察完食堂后，彭总问刘孟晋：</SPAN><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">你说真心话，这么多人在一起吃饭好，还是自己做饭吃好？共产主义绝不是吃大锅饭</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">。刘孟晋说：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">当然自己做饭方便。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">时隔一年，刘孟晋被下放到杨家桥任大队书记，他带头解散了食堂。</SPAN><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=EN-US>1959</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">反右</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">时，就成了他右倾机会主义反党的</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">罪证</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">之一。</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT face=宋体><FONT size=3><st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"2010\" Month=\"10\" Day=\"24\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\"><SPAN lang=EN-US>10</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>24</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">上午，彭总和县委的部分同志合影留念。并将年仅</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>28</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">岁的敦煌县委副书记拉在自己身旁一起照相。</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">中午，给彭总上了敦煌人招待亲戚的</SPAN><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">稍子面</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">。饭菜非常简单，彭总吃得很高兴。他对刘孟晋说：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">前两天你对我是搞特殊，今天才是家常便饭。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">下午，刘孟晋陪同彭总参观敦煌莫高窟。沿途看到一些土法炼铁的炉子，彭总说：</SPAN><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">这样的炉子怎么能炼铁呢？能办到的事就办，办不到不要硬办。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">在路上，彭总坐在吉普车后坐的中间，张达志司令员坐右边，刘孟晋坐在左边。彭总看到刘孟晋，端端正正的坐在座垫上，身子未躺在靠背上，彭总笑道：</SPAN><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">躺在靠背上多舒服，那样坐多难受，你这年轻人！</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">。听到彭总的话，刘孟晋内心激起了万分感激的心情，他感到格外亲切、温暖和更加由衷的敬佩！</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">在莫高窟参观时，彭总发现了保卫人员，马上对刘孟晋说：</SPAN><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">孟晋啊，这又是你搞的一套，不要神秘，搞过分了就要脱离群众。</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">彭总便参观便说：</SPAN><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">这是国宝，一千多年了，能保存下来很不容易，破坏也不少，这要好好维修，把它好好的保存下来。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">在那个</SPAN><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=EN-US>1958</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年的秋天的下午，彭总的吉普车驶离了敦煌，渐渐的消失在人们的视野里。</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">然而，闹剧任然在上演。</SPAN><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=EN-US>1958</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年底，敦煌又放出了甘肃全省第一个棉花千斤县的卫星。全县还出现了亩产</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>8719.15</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">斤籽棉的高产棉田。敦煌实现了</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">把全国粮、棉大面积丰产旗帜插在敦煌土地上</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">的战斗口号，以创造粮棉双千斤县的</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">奇迹</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">，名列全国农业先进单位，受到了国务院的最高嘉奖。</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">实际情况是，敦煌</SPAN><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=EN-US>1958</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年小麦亩产不是</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>1037</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">斤，而是</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>337</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">斤，多报</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>700</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">斤。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>1958</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年棉花亩产籽棉不是</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>1005</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">斤，而是</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>213</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">斤，多报</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>792</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">斤。其中，还有不少</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">元帅</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">升帐，成群</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">卫星</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">上天。如洋芋亩产</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>45580</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">斤，高粱亩产</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>3276</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">斤，谷子亩产</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>3080</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">斤等等。</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">导致的后果是，</SPAN><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=EN-US>1960</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年冬至</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>1961</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年春，敦煌大批牲畜死亡，人口大量外流，饥饿死亡蔓延。据统计，敦煌全县总人口由</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>1959</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年的</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>91257</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">人下降为</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>1960</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年的</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>84843</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">人，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>1961</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年全县人口下降为，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>65668</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">人。两年全县减少人口</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>25589</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">人。其中，外流</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>7361</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">人，死亡</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>3112</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">人。</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">当年的</SPAN><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: ","title":"彭德怀来敦煌的真实秘密","time":1285435658999}